{
  "page": "Warden of the Sands",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #DEDEE2; text-align:center;\">Warden of the Sands</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Office</th><td>\nRuler of <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Region</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Seven_Kingdoms\" title=\"Seven Kingdoms\">Seven Kingdoms</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Current Holder</th><td>\nNone</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">First Holder</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Rosby\" title=\"Jon Rosby\">Jon Rosby</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Last Holder</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Rosby\" title=\"Jon Rosby\">Jon Rosby</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Creator</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">Aegon I Targaryen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Created</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/First_Dornish_War\" title=\"First Dornish War\">First Dornish War</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Defunct</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/5_AC\" title=\"5 AC\">5&#160;AC</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Warden of the Sands</b> is a defunct <a href=\"/index.php/Warden\" title=\"Warden\">warden</a> title devised by <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">Aegon I Targaryen</a> during the brief occupation of <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a> by the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/First_Dornish_War\" title=\"First Dornish War\">First Dornish War</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Warden_of_the_Sands&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>When King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">Aegon I Targaryen</a> left Dorne to return to <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>, he named Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Rosby\" title=\"Jon Rosby\">Jon Rosby</a> the <a href=\"/index.php/Castellan\" title=\"Castellan\">Castellan</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Sunspear\" title=\"Sunspear\">Sunspear</a> and the Warden of the Sands. The <a href=\"/index.php/Dornishmen\" title=\"Dornishmen\">Dornishmen</a> soon rebelled, however, and Rosby was killed in the <a href=\"/index.php/Defenestration_of_Sunspear\" title=\"Defenestration of Sunspear\">Defenestration of Sunspear</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_dorne:_dorne_against_the_dragons.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_dorne:_dorne_against_the_dragons.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Warden_of_the_Sands&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Conquest_of_Dorne\" title=\"Conquest of Dorne\">Conquest of Dorne</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Prince_of_Dorne\" title=\"Prince of Dorne\">Prince of Dorne</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Warden_of_the_Sands&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References